1
00:00:00,602 --> 00:00:03,840
<i>♫ The dusk awakens ♫</i>

2
00:00:04,736 --> 00:00:08,320
<i>♫ The slumber of the whales ♫</i>

3
00:00:11,840 --> 00:00:15,168
<i>♫ Swimming towards the galaxy ♫</i>

4
00:00:16,096 --> 00:00:20,960
<i>♫ It docks at the blue shore of my heart ♫</i>

5
00:00:20,960 --> 00:00:25,952
<i>♫ I hear the poems coming from afar ♫</i>

6
00:00:26,592 --> 00:00:32,192
<i>♫ Happiness and sorrow come and go ♫</i>

7
00:00:32,192 --> 00:00:37,760
<i>♫ As my memories dance along the clouds ♫</i>

8
00:00:37,760 --> 00:00:41,568
<i>♫ I still remember ♫</i>

9
00:00:43,392 --> 00:00:49,184
<i>♫ Please wait for me at the horizon ♫</i>

10
00:00:49,184 --> 00:00:52,448
<i>♫ We'll watch the sunset together ♫</i>

11
00:00:54,688 --> 00:01:00,320
<i>♫ Whose dream hasn't been beautiful ♫</i>

12
00:01:00,320 --> 00:01:04,480
<i>♫ When have I ever been myself ♫</i>

13
00:01:06,048 --> 00:01:11,808
<i>♫ Wait for me at the end of the daydream ♫</i>

14
00:01:11,808 --> 00:01:15,232
<i>♫ Who has wandered within it ♫</i>

15
00:01:17,312 --> 00:01:22,272
<i>♫ Life is nothing more than fantasy ♫</i>

16
00:01:23,136 --> 00:01:25,466
<i>♫ I am still me ♫</i>

17
00:01:25,466 --> 00:01:29,658
<i>[You Are Desire]</i>

18
00:01:29,658 --> 00:01:33,754
<i>[Episode 10 Everyone's Dream Can Come True]</i>

19
00:01:34,272 --> 00:01:35,392
Lin Yujing!

20
00:01:38,400 --> 00:01:40,480
This way! Your mom is here.

21
00:01:47,840 --> 00:01:49,280
This is…

22
00:01:50,464 --> 00:01:51,616
Your mom?

23
00:02:00,672 --> 00:02:01,728
Why are you here?

24
00:02:01,728 --> 00:02:03,040
To check on you, of course.

25
00:02:04,448 --> 00:02:05,888
We're about to hold a parents' meeting.

26
00:02:05,888 --> 00:02:08,840
Since your mom's here,
I'll talk with her about your situation.

27
00:02:12,128 --> 00:02:13,360
Lin Yujing,

28
00:02:13,984 --> 00:02:15,808
didn't you ask me
to come to the parents' meeting?

29
00:02:16,416 --> 00:02:17,759
Who is this?

30
00:02:19,392 --> 00:02:20,400
I am her brother.

31
00:02:27,104 --> 00:02:28,199
Where's your seat?

32
00:02:30,240 --> 00:02:32,064
The parents' meeting is about to start.

33
00:02:32,064 --> 00:02:33,984
Well, you should go inside.

34
00:02:33,984 --> 00:02:36,032
We'll talk about the rest after the meeting.

35
00:02:36,736 --> 00:02:37,760
Okay?

36
00:02:51,104 --> 00:02:54,880
I'd like to talk about
our new transfer student,

37
00:02:55,706 --> 00:02:56,768
Lin Yujing.

38
00:02:57,625 --> 00:03:00,384
She is a role model for our class.

39
00:03:00,384 --> 00:03:02,176
Not only does she have good grades,

40
00:03:02,176 --> 00:03:03,936
but she also motivates her peers

41
00:03:03,936 --> 00:03:05,824
to progress and improve together.

42
00:03:06,426 --> 00:03:07,776
Everyone likes her a lot.

43
00:03:13,505 --> 00:03:14,752
Who is that woman?

44
00:03:15,546 --> 00:03:16,768
She looks pretty good.

45
00:03:17,665 --> 00:03:20,266
Why does she look like…

46
00:03:20,785 --> 00:03:22,505
Did you ask both of your parents to come over?

47
00:03:23,945 --> 00:03:25,626
Hey! Why did you hit me?

48
00:03:25,626 --> 00:03:26,746
Can you be quiet?

49
00:03:49,266 --> 00:03:50,845
<i>Didn't we agree?</i>

50
00:03:50,845 --> 00:03:52,986
<i>You'll stay in Pucheng for a few days.</i>

51
00:03:54,706 --> 00:03:56,746
<i>You've always liked this bracelet, right?</i>

52
00:03:57,465 --> 00:03:58,586
<i>It's yours now.</i>

53
00:04:00,426 --> 00:04:03,385
<i>She's the one who did all of this.</i>

54
00:04:04,625 --> 00:04:05,984
<i>And she didn't let me tell you.</i>

55
00:04:06,560 --> 00:04:09,145
<i>Yu, you'll stay with your dad for some days.</i>

56
00:04:09,145 --> 00:04:11,426
<i>So you tricked me into coming to Pucheng.</i>

57
00:04:11,426 --> 00:04:13,066
<i>You two planned it behind my back, right?</i>

58
00:04:13,066 --> 00:04:14,848
<i>I did this for your own good.</i>

59
00:04:15,746 --> 00:04:16,928
<i>You'll understand later.</i>

60
00:04:17,466 --> 00:04:19,705
<i>When you guys divorced,
you said you wanted me to live with you.</i>

61
00:04:20,306 --> 00:04:21,825
<i>I thought you loved me.</i>

62
00:04:22,866 --> 00:04:24,106
<i>Now you also abandoned me.</i>

63
00:04:25,385 --> 00:04:27,065
<i>I'm completely homeless.</i>

64
00:04:36,825 --> 00:04:38,112
Your mom came here to see you.

65
00:04:39,585 --> 00:04:40,896
Aren't you happy?

66
00:04:47,226 --> 00:04:49,024
I didn't expect her to come suddenly.

67
00:04:49,786 --> 00:04:52,672
I thought she had abandoned me.

68
00:05:10,385 --> 00:05:11,392
How was it?

69
00:05:14,065 --> 00:05:15,392
You and your mom are quite alike.

70
00:05:16,065 --> 00:05:17,216
I didn't ask about her!

71
00:05:17,216 --> 00:05:18,368
I mean the parents' meeting.

72
00:05:20,825 --> 00:05:23,104
Your homeroom teacher spoke highly of you.

73
00:05:23,104 --> 00:05:24,800
Your mom is chatting with him inside.

74
00:05:26,466 --> 00:05:27,825
It seems like she cares about you a lot.

75
00:05:29,986 --> 00:05:31,306
So, I decided to come out.

76
00:05:31,306 --> 00:05:33,152
After all, I'm just an outsider.

77
00:05:35,168 --> 00:05:36,672
Thanks, bro.

78
00:05:37,856 --> 00:05:39,232
Where's Shen Juan?

79
00:05:39,232 --> 00:05:40,608
Why isn't he with you?

80
00:05:40,608 --> 00:05:42,528
He already left. He had something to do.

81
00:05:43,546 --> 00:05:44,786
Alright, I'm leaving.

82
00:05:47,825 --> 00:05:49,986
Don't tell Meng Weiguo about today.

83
00:05:51,585 --> 00:05:52,926
What do I have to say to him?

84
00:05:52,926 --> 00:05:54,016
Bye.

85
00:05:59,746 --> 00:06:02,176
You don't need to worry about her study.

86
00:06:03,025 --> 00:06:04,480
Oh, there she is. I'll be leaving.

87
00:06:05,226 --> 00:06:06,720
- Thank you.
- You're welcome.

88
00:06:14,176 --> 00:06:15,666
Look at your grades!

89
00:06:15,666 --> 00:06:17,152
You only got
the second-highest score of your class.

90
00:06:17,696 --> 00:06:19,520
You were always the best in your class before.

91
00:06:20,746 --> 00:06:22,226
I also heard that you are now living on campus.

92
00:06:22,786 --> 00:06:24,544
How could Meng Weiguo treat you like this?

93
00:06:25,866 --> 00:06:27,584
I think I'm doing just fine.

94
00:06:28,185 --> 00:06:29,216
I'm enjoying my study,

95
00:06:29,216 --> 00:06:30,400
and I feel happy to live here.

96
00:06:31,168 --> 00:06:32,352
Is that so?

97
00:06:32,352 --> 00:06:33,792
Haven't you already abandoned me?

98
00:06:33,792 --> 00:06:35,025
Why do you still care?

99
00:06:37,265 --> 00:06:38,986
When did I abandon you?

100
00:06:39,705 --> 00:06:41,536
Then why did you let me live with Meng Weiguo?

101
00:06:41,536 --> 00:06:43,200
You haven't even cared about me for ages.

102
00:06:43,904 --> 00:06:45,504
I'm doing pretty well now.

103
00:06:45,504 --> 00:06:47,456
And I'm satisfied with my grades.

104
00:06:49,825 --> 00:06:51,840
Do you have to be so aggressive,

105
00:06:51,840 --> 00:06:52,992
Lin Yujing?

106
00:06:52,992 --> 00:06:54,240
Are you done?

107
00:06:55,025 --> 00:06:56,306
May I leave, then?

108
00:06:57,746 --> 00:06:59,648
Thank you for coming.

109
00:06:59,648 --> 00:07:01,248
But honestly, it isn't necessary.

110
00:07:18,065 --> 00:07:19,424
Hello, who are you looking for?

111
00:07:19,424 --> 00:07:20,736
Lin Yujing.

112
00:07:21,760 --> 00:07:23,296
Please come in.

113
00:07:37,696 --> 00:07:39,424
I've told your teacher.

114
00:07:39,424 --> 00:07:41,376
You'll stay with me for a few days.

115
00:07:42,848 --> 00:07:43,936
I won't.

116
00:07:43,936 --> 00:07:45,440
I just moved in here.

117
00:07:45,440 --> 00:07:46,592
And I'm doing just fine.

118
00:07:46,592 --> 00:07:48,096
Pack your things now.

119
00:07:48,096 --> 00:07:49,248
I'll wait for you at the door.

120
00:07:49,906 --> 00:07:51,744
I said I won't!

121
00:07:57,705 --> 00:07:59,584
I'll give you twenty minutes.

122
00:07:59,584 --> 00:08:00,992
Hurry up and get packed.

123
00:08:12,065 --> 00:08:13,440
Are you okay?

124
00:08:15,424 --> 00:08:16,512
I'm fine.

125
00:08:56,746 --> 00:08:58,765
<i>Lin Yujing's mother suddenly came.</i>

126
00:08:58,765 --> 00:09:01,145
<i>She insisted on
asking Yujing to live with her for a few days.</i>

127
00:09:01,706 --> 00:09:03,246
<i>She didn't seem happy.</i>

128
00:09:03,246 --> 00:09:04,768
<i>I'm quite worried.</i>

129
00:09:15,648 --> 00:09:18,880
Sorry, the number you have dialed
is temporarily unavailable.

130
00:09:18,880 --> 00:09:20,736
Please try again later.

131
00:09:24,192 --> 00:09:25,920
We'll stay here for a few days.

132
00:09:30,466 --> 00:09:31,744
How long?

133
00:09:31,744 --> 00:09:33,696
I have to go back to the dormitory.

134
00:09:36,866 --> 00:09:38,272
Who agreed to let you live on campus?

135
00:09:39,488 --> 00:09:40,926
I asked your teacher.

136
00:09:40,926 --> 00:09:43,328
It requires the consent of a guardian.

137
00:09:43,328 --> 00:09:44,544
My dad.

138
00:09:44,544 --> 00:09:45,952
Your dad?

139
00:09:47,466 --> 00:09:48,544
I also asked him.

140
00:09:49,265 --> 00:09:50,785
He never agreed to let you live on campus.

141
00:09:51,346 --> 00:09:52,768
You made the decision on your own.

142
00:09:54,625 --> 00:09:56,096
I earned enough money to pay for it.

143
00:09:56,096 --> 00:09:57,376
I feel happy living there.

144
00:09:58,025 --> 00:09:59,392
You earned money?

145
00:10:02,346 --> 00:10:04,064
Didn't Meng Weiguo give you money?

146
00:10:18,784 --> 00:10:21,206
Lin Yujing, I called you several times.

147
00:10:21,206 --> 00:10:22,496
Why didn't you answer?

148
00:10:22,496 --> 00:10:24,608
Do you think you have someone to back you up

149
00:10:24,608 --> 00:10:25,856
since your mother is back?

150
00:10:28,385 --> 00:10:29,856
Let me tell you.

151
00:10:29,856 --> 00:10:31,625
You're living with me now.

152
00:10:32,128 --> 00:10:33,152
I warn you.

153
00:10:33,152 --> 00:10:34,688
When you're with your mother,

154
00:10:35,200 --> 00:10:37,286
you should know what to say

155
00:10:37,286 --> 00:10:38,720
and what not to say.

156
00:10:39,712 --> 00:10:40,736
What to say

157
00:10:40,736 --> 00:10:41,952
and what not to say?

158
00:10:41,952 --> 00:10:44,224
Explain your words, Meng Weiguo.

159
00:10:45,472 --> 00:10:47,306
I have nothing to say to you.

160
00:10:47,306 --> 00:10:48,646
We'll meet tomorrow.

161
00:10:48,646 --> 00:10:50,080
You have to explain to me.

162
00:10:55,584 --> 00:10:57,216
What has Meng Weiguo done to you?

163
00:11:10,025 --> 00:11:11,712
<i>I heard from Xu Ruyi.</i>

164
00:11:12,385 --> 00:11:14,048
<i>Your mother wants you
to live with her for a few days.</i>

165
00:11:15,776 --> 00:11:17,664
<i>I'll go back to my dorm tomorrow.</i>

166
00:11:19,385 --> 00:11:20,928
<i>Do you need help?</i>

167
00:11:23,008 --> 00:11:24,064
<i>No.</i>

168
00:11:28,608 --> 00:11:30,866
Mr. Zhang, I've received the contract.

169
00:11:33,568 --> 00:11:35,136
Thank you, Mr. Zhang.

170
00:11:53,216 --> 00:11:54,465
Hurry up! Hurry!

171
00:11:54,465 --> 00:11:55,680
Wait for me!

172
00:12:18,785 --> 00:12:20,000
Good morning, deskmate.

173
00:12:21,385 --> 00:12:22,688
Good morning, deskmate.

174
00:12:24,928 --> 00:12:26,826
My dad gave me some pocket money yesterday.

175
00:12:27,346 --> 00:12:28,640
Liu said,

176
00:12:28,640 --> 00:12:30,866
"Wang Yiyang did pretty well this semester."

177
00:12:30,866 --> 00:12:32,320
My old man was so happy.

178
00:12:34,016 --> 00:12:35,264
Your dad is so kind to you.

179
00:12:35,264 --> 00:12:36,352
As soon as I went back,

180
00:12:36,352 --> 00:12:38,365
my mom put a few goji berries in my cup

181
00:12:38,365 --> 00:12:39,936
and told me to do better next time.

182
00:12:40,960 --> 00:12:42,746
Lin Yujing, what about you?

183
00:12:42,746 --> 00:12:44,960
Did your mom give you any reward?

184
00:12:44,960 --> 00:12:46,624
Mind your own business.

185
00:12:46,624 --> 00:12:48,864
Hey, come on! We're so close.

186
00:12:48,864 --> 00:12:50,080
What can't you tell me about?

187
00:12:50,080 --> 00:12:51,104
Turn around.

188
00:13:01,586 --> 00:13:04,512
Our last parents' meeting was very successful.

189
00:13:05,024 --> 00:13:06,066
Alas, don't bring that up.

190
00:13:06,066 --> 00:13:07,746
My dad scolded me when he got home.

191
00:13:08,505 --> 00:13:10,880
I know you've been studying hard.

192
00:13:12,466 --> 00:13:15,648
But you should also pay more attention
to communicating with your parents.

193
00:13:16,960 --> 00:13:18,016
Okay?

194
00:13:18,016 --> 00:13:20,896
Okay.

195
00:13:21,425 --> 00:13:23,776
Alright, let's start the class.

196
00:13:45,824 --> 00:13:46,912
Have you eaten?

197
00:13:47,520 --> 00:13:48,896
I'm not hungry.

198
00:13:58,706 --> 00:14:00,166
That doesn't seem right.

199
00:14:00,166 --> 00:14:01,920
Why did you buy peanuts?

200
00:14:05,346 --> 00:14:06,946
You told me before.

201
00:14:07,986 --> 00:14:09,106
No matter what happens,

202
00:14:09,986 --> 00:14:11,346
I still have to eat well.

203
00:14:18,665 --> 00:14:19,808
In the future,

204
00:14:20,385 --> 00:14:21,984
if there's something
you don't want to tell me about,

205
00:14:22,706 --> 00:14:23,712
you don't have to say it.

206
00:14:23,712 --> 00:14:25,248
I won't ask you, either.

207
00:14:25,248 --> 00:14:26,528
But you should never fool me.

208
00:14:28,746 --> 00:14:30,624
When have I ever fooled you?

209
00:14:31,586 --> 00:14:32,866
Whenever you felt guilty,

210
00:14:32,866 --> 00:14:34,186
you always sent that emoji.

211
00:14:37,024 --> 00:14:38,926
Well, my mom came so suddenly,

212
00:14:38,926 --> 00:14:40,608
so I can't quite accept the situation.

213
00:14:40,608 --> 00:14:42,656
I'll be fine in a few days. Don't worry.

214
00:15:10,826 --> 00:15:14,656
I didn't expect this place to be so formal.

215
00:15:15,168 --> 00:15:17,184
Don't overthink. I just finished a meeting.

216
00:15:18,464 --> 00:15:19,525
Just say what you need to say.

217
00:15:19,525 --> 00:15:21,920
Let me ask you. Why did you beat Yu?

218
00:15:23,296 --> 00:15:25,248
You can't imagine how she spoke to me.

219
00:15:25,248 --> 00:15:27,026
Do you know how much you've spoiled her?

220
00:15:27,026 --> 00:15:29,184
That's not an excuse. She's your daughter!

221
00:15:29,184 --> 00:15:31,008
You can't just beat her like that.

222
00:15:31,008 --> 00:15:32,385
Ever since she moved in with me

223
00:15:33,106 --> 00:15:34,326
she hasn't given me a moment's peace.

224
00:15:34,326 --> 00:15:35,840
She's always opposing me.

225
00:15:36,425 --> 00:15:39,104
Lin Zhi, are you instigating her
behind my back?

226
00:15:40,066 --> 00:15:41,408
Instigating? Me?

227
00:15:42,304 --> 00:15:43,648
Don't play dumb with me.

228
00:15:45,946 --> 00:15:47,808
If neither of us gave her money,

229
00:15:47,808 --> 00:15:49,696
how could she be able to live on campus?

230
00:15:52,505 --> 00:15:54,046
You didn't know about this?

231
00:15:54,046 --> 00:15:56,032
She earned it on her own.

232
00:15:56,586 --> 00:15:57,726
How did you discipline her?

233
00:15:57,726 --> 00:15:58,866
How did you look after her?

234
00:15:58,866 --> 00:15:59,905
How?

235
00:16:01,664 --> 00:16:04,672
I've topped up her campus card
and transportation card.

236
00:16:05,178 --> 00:16:06,432
It's enough for her to live on.

237
00:16:07,305 --> 00:16:08,785
She's already out of control without any money.

238
00:16:08,785 --> 00:16:09,792
What if she has enough money?

239
00:16:09,792 --> 00:16:11,106
What would she do?

240
00:16:11,106 --> 00:16:12,352
Money, money, money.

241
00:16:15,346 --> 00:16:17,166
You're still the same as before.

242
00:16:17,166 --> 00:16:18,946
After all these years,
you haven't changed at all.

243
00:16:20,672 --> 00:16:23,040
Lin Zhi, I-I don't want to argue with you.

244
00:16:23,866 --> 00:16:24,928
Just say it. What do you want?

245
00:16:26,066 --> 00:16:28,145
I asked you to come here for only one reason.

246
00:16:28,706 --> 00:16:30,826
I will take Yu back to Huaicheng.

247
00:16:51,145 --> 00:16:53,632
I heard your mom came to Pucheng.

248
00:16:54,986 --> 00:16:56,345
She asked me to stay with her for a few days.

249
00:16:56,345 --> 00:16:57,856
And she wants to negotiate with Meng Weiguo.

250
00:16:58,746 --> 00:17:00,928
She's not planning to take you back, is she?

251
00:17:02,305 --> 00:17:03,346
She can't.

252
00:17:05,626 --> 00:17:06,886
It's not that simple.

253
00:17:06,886 --> 00:17:08,000
Let's meet and talk about it.

254
00:17:16,146 --> 00:17:17,760
My mom told me something.

255
00:17:17,760 --> 00:17:20,384
She said that
your mother sent you to your dad's

256
00:17:20,928 --> 00:17:22,208
because of some issues with her company.

257
00:17:23,520 --> 00:17:25,792
I think she did it to protect you.

258
00:17:32,545 --> 00:17:35,104
But don't worry too much.

259
00:17:35,104 --> 00:17:36,448
I also heard that

260
00:17:36,448 --> 00:17:39,265
she has already found an investor in Huaicheng

261
00:17:59,392 --> 00:18:01,120
Did you send me here

262
00:18:01,825 --> 00:18:03,712
because your company was in trouble?

263
00:18:12,386 --> 00:18:13,666
Who told you that?

264
00:18:14,426 --> 00:18:15,646
