<i>♫ I hear the poems coming from afar ♫</i>

528
00:37:20,442 --> 00:37:26,042
<i>♫ Happiness and sorrow come and go ♫</i>

529
00:37:26,042 --> 00:37:31,610
<i>♫ As my memories dance along the clouds ♫</i>

530
00:37:31,610 --> 00:37:35,418
<i>♫ I still remember ♫</i>

531
00:37:37,242 --> 00:37:43,034
<i>♫ Please wait for me at the horizon ♫</i>

532
00:37:43,034 --> 00:37:46,298
<i>♫ We'll watch the sunset together ♫</i>

533
00:37:48,538 --> 00:37:54,272
<i>♫ Whose dream hasn't been beautiful ♫</i>

534
00:37:54,272 --> 00:37:55,712
Happy New Year.

535
00:37:57,066 --> 00:37:58,464
Happy New Year.

536
00:37:59,898 --> 00:38:05,658
<i>♫ Wait for me at the end of the daydream ♫</i>

537
00:38:05,658 --> 00:38:09,082
<i>♫ Who has wandered within it ♫</i>

538
00:38:11,162 --> 00:38:16,122
<i>♫ Life is nothing more than fantasy ♫</i>

539
00:38:16,986 --> 00:38:20,992
<i>♫ I am still me ♫</i>

540
00:38:31,706 --> 00:38:33,586
I had a great time today.

541
00:38:34,146 --> 00:38:35,936
Thank you for your hospitality, Ms. Lin.

542
00:38:36,465 --> 00:38:37,766
You're welcome.

543
00:38:37,766 --> 00:38:39,606
After the New Year, I'll have my colleagues

544
00:38:39,606 --> 00:38:41,206
coordinate the details with your people.

545
00:38:41,206 --> 00:38:42,432
Okay.

546
00:38:42,432 --> 00:38:43,648
Goodbye.

547
00:39:03,008 --> 00:39:05,056
Go back and rest early.

548
00:39:06,506 --> 00:39:07,584
Okay.

549
00:39:08,096 --> 00:39:09,568
Send me a message when you get home.

550
00:39:12,626 --> 00:39:14,026
- I'm leaving.
- Bye.

551
00:39:14,546 --> 00:39:16,128
Bye.

552
00:39:54,144 --> 00:39:56,352
The only reason that I came here

553
00:39:56,896 --> 00:39:58,208
is to take you back.

554
00:39:59,226 --> 00:40:00,945
After this semester ends,

555
00:40:01,465 --> 00:40:02,945
you'll go back to Huaicheng with me.

556
00:40:22,865 --> 00:40:24,106
What do you mean

557
00:40:24,106 --> 00:40:25,746
by taking me back to Huaicheng?

558
00:40:25,746 --> 00:40:27,328
Have you ever asked for my opinion?

559
00:40:29,666 --> 00:40:31,345
Didn't you want to go back to Huaicheng before?

560
00:40:32,186 --> 00:40:33,446
Yeah. Before.

561
00:40:33,446 --> 00:40:34,566
But I don't want to go back now.

562
00:40:34,566 --> 00:40:35,872
I like it here.

563
00:40:37,888 --> 00:40:39,392
What exactly do you like?

564
00:40:40,106 --> 00:40:41,506
Everything.

565
00:40:42,465 --> 00:40:44,046
I like the weather here.

566
00:40:44,046 --> 00:40:45,746
I like the roads here.

567
00:40:45,746 --> 00:40:46,784
I like the breakfast here.

568
00:40:46,784 --> 00:40:47,808
I like the people here.

569
00:40:47,808 --> 00:40:48,960
I don't want to leave now.

570
00:40:51,666 --> 00:40:53,026
The people?

571
00:40:54,506 --> 00:40:55,840
You're really sensible.

572
00:40:57,425 --> 00:40:58,766
It's settled.

573
00:40:58,766 --> 00:41:00,192
You must go back with me.

574
00:41:01,066 --> 00:41:02,546
What if I refuse?

575
00:41:02,546 --> 00:41:04,384
Are you going to force me?

576
00:41:11,392 --> 00:41:14,592
Lin Yujing, what are you talking about?

577
00:41:14,592 --> 00:41:15,808
Did I say it wrong?

578
00:41:16,905 --> 00:41:18,240
Since my childhood,

579
00:41:19,026 --> 00:41:21,216
when have you ever followed my wishes?

580
00:41:24,465 --> 00:41:25,945
You've been living as you wish

581
00:41:26,546 --> 00:41:28,864
since your dad has never disciplined you.

582
00:41:28,864 --> 00:41:30,265
Look at you now.

583
00:41:31,146 --> 00:41:32,406
You're about to
take the college entrance exam in a year.

584
00:41:32,406 --> 00:41:34,048
Yet your grades are falling,

585
00:41:34,048 --> 00:41:36,096
and you hang out until midnight
before coming home.

586
00:41:48,586 --> 00:41:50,186
Let me make it clear to you, Lin Yujing,

587
00:41:50,985 --> 00:41:52,425
I'm not giving you a choice.

588
00:42:21,746 --> 00:42:23,552
<i>Happy New Year, Shen Juan.</i>

589
00:42:27,232 --> 00:42:29,600
<i>Happy New Year, Lin Yujing.</i>

590
00:42:43,066 --> 00:42:47,610
<i>♫ Love sprouts in my palm ♫</i>

591
00:42:48,922 --> 00:42:52,762
<i>♫ Yet worried linger within my eyes ♫</i>

592
00:42:54,554 --> 00:42:59,130
<i>♫ Our story hasn't ended ♫</i>

593
00:43:00,058 --> 00:43:03,738
<i>♫ So where are we now ♫</i>

594
00:43:05,562 --> 00:43:11,226
<i>♫ I want to hug you so badly ♫</i>

595
00:43:11,226 --> 00:43:15,290
<i>♫ I want to become better with you ♫</i>

596
00:43:16,538 --> 00:43:21,402
<i>♫ The youth we shared ♫</i>

597
00:43:21,402 --> 00:43:27,450
<i>♫ Turned into a rainbow within my heart ♫</i>

598
00:43:27,962 --> 00:43:33,530
<i>♫ I really want to warm you ♫</i>

599
00:43:33,530 --> 00:43:35,418
<i>♫ I want to share with you ♫</i>

600
00:43:35,418 --> 00:43:40,090
<i>♫ The beauty of the world ♫</i>

601
00:43:40,974 --> 00:43:43,194
<i>♫ We promised ♫</i>

602
00:43:43,770 --> 00:43:49,466
<i>♫ To never be apart ♫</i>

603
00:43:50,202 --> 00:43:55,904
<i>♫ Do you want to hear me sing ♫</i>

604
00:43:55,904 --> 00:44:00,666
<i>♫ The wind chime swaying in my heart ♫</i>

605
00:44:01,210 --> 00:44:05,434
<i>♫ Is a wish ♫</i>

606
00:44:06,170 --> 00:44:12,058
<i>♫ I secretly made for you ♫</i>

607
00:44:12,602 --> 00:44:18,138
<i>♫ I want to plant ♫</i>

608
00:44:18,138 --> 00:44:20,026
<i>♫ A red maple forest ♫</i>

609
00:44:20,026 --> 00:44:24,634
<i>♫ To dye the whole mountain red ♫</i>

610
00:44:25,562 --> 00:44:27,802
<i>♫ The sky after the rain ♫</i>

611
00:44:28,442 --> 00:44:33,370
<i>♫ Was painted by our brilliant dreams ♫</i>

612
00:44:40,250 --> 00:44:45,018
<i>♫ Time is a flower of dream ♫</i>

613
00:44:45,850 --> 00:44:50,936
<i>♫ You've already collected it ♫</i>

614
00:44:51,866 --> 00:44:55,866
<i>♫ When we all become better ♫</i>

615
00:44:57,338 --> 00:45:01,466
<i>♫ We'll see the best of the world together ♫</i>
